title: The One With No Topic III
description:
This week Bob and Monét bring you THE ONE WITH NO TOPIC III!! In reaction to Kim K's public statement regarding work ethic, Bob and Monét answer the question, "what is hard work?" Monét admits she fantasizes about fighting Bob and Bob asks the question, "would Monét stand by me if I got cancelled?". You won't want to miss this chaotic episode!
